update() method update the value in documents
save() method replace the documents by replacing data

db.user.update({"name":"Ram"},{$set:{"name":"dhaker"}})
WriteResult({ "nMatched" : 1, "nUpserted" : 0, "nModified" :..............

//it only update the single value
to update multiple value

db.user.update({"name":"Ram"},{$set:{"name":"dhaker"}},{multi:true})
WriteResult({ "nMatched" : 3, "nUpserted" : 0, "nModified" : 3 })




